data.description: Immaculate 4bedrooms, 3bath home in the well sought after Sterling on the Lake. All upgraded cabinets, hardwood floors, inviting upgraded fireplace, Kitchen features an oversized island, gas range, grey glass backsplash, and large pantry! Owner's suite bright and spacious, huge walk-in closet, and a SPA like spacious bathroom with double sinks, walk in shower with a designer touch.  Enjoy those beautiful autumn evenings watching the birds with the well designed pergola.
